@startuml gkg_deploy_saas
!include gkg_common.puml

title Deployment: GitLab.com (Multi-tenant SaaS)

' ===================================================================
' SAAS-SPECIFIC: ClickHouse Cloud, consumers, billing
' ===================================================================
actor "**LLM Agents**\nvia DAP" as agents #F3E5F5

database "**ClickHouse Cloud**\nCode + SDLC data lake\n(per-tenant schema)" as ch #d09191

' Data layer connections
sdlc_idx --> ch : TCP native (write)
code_idx --> ch : TCP native (write)
query_eng --> ch : TCP native (read, parameterized SQL)

' Consumer -> monolith -> module
agents --> rails : HTTP (query_graph,\nget_graph_schema)

note bottom of module
  **Tenant isolation:** Per-tenant ClickHouse schema.
  Three-layer auth: org isolation (JWT), traversal
  filter (allowed paths from Rails in JWT), Rails redaction.

  **Billing:** Credit-based. Zero-rated for GitLab-driven
  queries, charged for customer-driven. Snowplow -> CDot.

  **Independent release:** Yes --- Orbit binary versioned
  separately from monolith.
end note

@enduml
